table></figure><div class="admonition note"><p class="admonition-title">Hexo-admonition</p><p>插件使用示例</p></div><div class="admonition warning"><p class="admonition-title">warning</p><p>测试</p></div><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>💕</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f495.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span></p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>❗</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2757.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>需要考虑的是</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⌚</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/231a.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
